of employees   capital ratio  website wwwcapitalonecom capital one bank in wake village texas capital one financial corporation is a bank holding company specializing in credit cards home loans auto loans banking and savings products headquartered in mclean virginia capital one is the eighthlargest commercial bank in the united states when ranked by assets and deposits and is ranked th on the list of largest banks in the united states by total assets the bank has  branches including  café style locations and  atms it is ranked  on the fortune   on fortunes  best companies to work for list and conducts business in the united states canada and the united kingdom the company helped pioneer the mass marketing of credit cards in the s and it is one of the largest customers of the united states postal service due to its direct mail credit card solicitations in  it was the th largest credit card issuer by purchase volume after american express jp morgan chase bank of america and citigroup capital one is also the th largest bank auto lender with a market share of  in  in   of the companys revenues were from credit cards  was from consumer banking  was from commercial banking and  was from other contents  divisions  history  monoline credit card company   expansion into auto loans present  expansion into retail banking present  sports marketing  corporate citizenship  criticism and legal actions  fines for misleading customers to pay extra for services  automated dialing to customers phones   amendment to terms of use to allow personal visits  see also  references  external links divisionsedit activities announcing the opening of the capitalone  café in boston capital one operates  divisions as follows credit cards  capital one issues credit cards in the united states canada and the united kingdom as of december   after jp morgan chase and citigroup capital one was the rd largest credit card issuer with an outstanding receivables balance of  billion representing  of the tota