foundation inc a nonprofit organization privacy policy about wikipedia disclaimers contact wikipedia developers cookie statement mobile view capital bank financial corp private company information  bloomberg july    pm et banks company overview of capital bank financial corp snapshot people company overview capital bank financial corp operates as the bank holding company for capital bank corporation that provides various commercial and consumer banking products and services and ancillary financial services to individuals and businesses in the southeastern region of the united states it offers various deposit products such as noninterestbearing checking interestbearing checking savings money market deposit and individual retirement accounts and certificates of deposit the company also provides commercial loan products including owner and nonowner occupied commercial real estate loans working capital loans and lines of credit demand construction and time loans and equipment i capital bank financial corp operates as the bank holding company for capital bank corporation that provides various commercial and consumer banking products and services and ancillary financial services to individuals and businesses in the southeastern region of the united states it offers various deposit products such as noninterestbearing checking interestbearing checking savings money market deposit and individual retirement accounts and certificates of deposit the company also provides commercial loan products including owner and nonowner occupied commercial real estate loans working capital loans and lines of credit demand construction and time loans and equipment inventory and accounts receivable financing in addition it offers consumer loan products comprising home equity loans and lines of credit residential first lien mortgages second lien mortgages new and used auto loans new and used boat loans overdraft protection and unsecured personal credit lines further the company provides debit 